# minimap
  https://github.com/dengste/minimap
ここ参考に https://qiita.com/betweens/items/ae85bd9bcf8ae48ea7e2
M-x package-install
  minimap
~/.emacs.d/init.el に追記
  (require 'minimap)
M-x customize-group
  minimap

